examination as well.

105
00:05:20,875 --> 00:05:24,750
So that brings you to a grand
total of ninety-four twenty.

106
00:05:25,958 --> 00:05:27,083
[NURSE 10A] You take care now!

107
00:05:27,166 --> 00:05:28,875
Right, thanks a lot.

108
00:05:29,208 --> 00:05:31,041
This month turned
out to be a bitch.

109
00:05:31,125 --> 00:05:32,625
Well, alright then.

110
00:05:32,708 --> 00:05:35,541
I've got no choice but to score
a big, fat bento the next time--

111
00:05:38,833 --> 00:05:41,166
Orthros?
Are you serious?

112
00:05:41,250 --> 00:05:42,875
This guy must
be incredibly strong.

113
00:05:42,958 --> 00:05:44,291
To say the least.

114
00:05:44,375 --> 00:05:46,416
And they've been popping
up a lot these past few days,

115
00:05:46,500 --> 00:05:49,625
randomly taking down
eastern wolves left and right.

116
00:05:54,791 --> 00:05:56,958
[NIKAIDO] Every Wolf
needs to be aware of this.

117
00:05:57,041 --> 00:05:58,041
[SHAGA] So, what?

118
00:05:58,125 --> 00:05:59,541
