128
00:06:21,125 --> 00:06:22,625
[NIKAIDO] It'd be great
if it were that easy,

129
00:06:22,708 --> 00:06:24,916
but none of Orthros'
victims are exactly helpful;

130
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:28,166
they all said the same thing
when I asked them about it.

131
00:06:28,250 --> 00:06:31,333
"The next thing I knew,
I was plunged into darkness."

132
00:06:31,916 --> 00:06:34,208
[NIKAIDO] In other words,
nobody can remember.

133
00:06:34,291 --> 00:06:37,750
