look like or how they fight.

134
00:06:37,833 --> 00:06:39,541
There's only one
thing we do know,

135
00:06:39,625 --> 00:06:42,541
Orthros is the nom de
guerre for a pack of two.

136
00:06:42,625 --> 00:06:44,166
Wait, a pack?

137
00:06:44,250 --> 00:06:47,291
So, you're saying
Orthros is two people?

138
00:06:47,375 --> 00:06:49,208
[NIKAIDO] Yeah, according
to the one person

139
00:06:49,291 --> 00:06:51,833
with some memory of their
attack, a Karasuda student who

140
00:06:51,916 --> 00:06:53,375
went to a brawl in the East,

141
00:06:53,458 --> 00:06:55,875
she was the last
victim I spoke with.

142
00:06:55,958 --> 00:06:57,083
[NIKAIDO] And she
heard something

143
00:06:57,166 --> 00:06:58,458
before she blacked out.

144
00:06:58,541 --> 00:07:01,041
[SAWAGI PRES] I think we
might've got the wrong girl.

145
00:07:01,125 --> 00:07:02,458
[SHAGA] The wrong girl?

146
00:07:02,541 --> 00:07:04,708
[NIKAIDO] And she had a
theory on why they said that.

147
00:07:04,791 --> 00:07:07,708
She said she's convinced Orthros
is searching for a particular

148
00:07:07,791 --> 00:07:10,916
Wolf whom they feel will
be a worthy opponent.

149
00:07:11,291 --> 00:07:13,666
[SHAGA] Why?
What do they want?

150
00:07:25,125 --> 00:07:26,541
Did you just
say the Monarch?

151
00:07:26,625 --> 00:07:29,625
[SATO] Yeah, all splayed out
in a store on the Eastside.

152
00:07:30,791 --> 00:07:33,416
I was kinda wonderin' if
you were the one behind it.

153
00:07:33,500 --> 00:07:36,083
And why the hell
would I do something like that?

154
00:07:40,750 --> 00:07:42,041
Dammit!

155
00:07:43,666 --> 00:07:45,250
So, hey, I was thinking.

156
00:07:45,333 --> 00:07:46,708
[SATO] Oh, yeah?

157
00:07:49,041 --> 00:07:50,208
Were you still
planning to go

158
00:07:50,291 --> 00:07:51,916
to a bento brawl tomorrow night?

159
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:53,250
[SATO] Mm-hmm.

160
00:07:54,291 --> 00:07:55,500
Why don't you
go to a supermarket

161
00:07:55,583 --> 00:07:56,791
on the Eastside for a change?

162
00:07:56,875 --> 00:07:59,791
[SATO] Nope.
Yarizui made a good point.

163
00:07:59,875 --> 00:08:00,916
[YARIZUI] Y'know, Sato.

164
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:02,583
If you wanna get
back to bento brawling,

165
00:08:02,666 --> 00:08:05,375
I think you should hit
up the Kamoshida Mart.

166
00:08:05,458 --> 00:08:07,333
There aren't any
high schools in that area,

167
00:08:07,416 --> 00:08:09,416
so your competition
should be light.

168
00:08:09,500 --> 00:08:11,541
It won't mess with
your healing too much.

169
00:08:11,625 --> 00:08:14,666
You should take it easy
until you're a hundred percent.

170
00:08:14,750 --> 00:08:15,916
That okay?

171
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:17,458
And that's
what I'm doing.

172
00:08:17,541 --> 00:08:20,000
It kinda sounded like she
might be worried about me.

173
00:08:20,083 --> 00:08:22,208
So it's the Kamoshida
Mart for me until--

174
00:08:24,500 --> 00:08:26,791
What?
No way!

175
00:08:26,875 --> 00:08:29,375
Bow before
your master, swine.

176
00:08:29,458 --> 00:08:31,250
[SATO] One more round!

177
00:08:31,333 --> 00:08:32,791
[SHAGA] Alright, drop dead.

178
00:08:32,875 --> 00:08:33,916
[Sato cries out]

179
