You got somethin'
on your mind, Oshiroi?

183
00:08:48,416 --> 00:08:50,583
[OSHIROI] Maybe if
Saito was actually a decoy.

184
00:08:50,666 --> 00:08:52,208
No, that's such a cliché.

185
00:08:52,291 --> 00:08:55,125
