[OSHIROI] And once
all of Saito's openings

189
00:09:00,041 --> 00:09:02,250
had been stuffed full--
wait, no, the lockers.

190
00:09:02,333 --> 00:09:03,666
I mean the lockers.

191
00:09:03,750 --> 00:09:05,916
Once Saito had been fully
stuffed inside the locker.

192
00:09:17,375 --> 00:09:19,875
[YARIZUI] Sato.
You gonna make your move?

193
00:09:19,958 --> 00:09:21,958
[SATO] Right.
Sorry.

194
00:09:24,875 --> 00:09:27,875
You're brawling tonight.
Give it your all.

195
00:09:27,958 --> 00:09:29,333
Oh, I'm planning on it.

196
